{
  "stem": "17543.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 233.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in, in this particular place, the corner shops which we bought food, it has been in a pre-printed forms which is on the door were stuck on-- dogs and Jews not allowed in.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I don't know where from we had the food really, must have somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- From there, we was collected up and had to go to an area, which is called ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody was all crammed up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So furniture and everything went-- we had to leave behind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, no-- no brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--but I had my mother's side grandmother lived in the same town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's brother lived in the same town, and my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my, my mother's brother [SOBBING] had a little daughter, four years old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And her name was Eva.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My little cousin-- I never saw her after that time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because all men had to go away to forced labor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know from what age to what age.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was difficult to get out of the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my aunty couldn't-- and we couldn't meet each other because they wasn't live very near.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my grandmother I couldn't see either, because we, we wasn't very near to each other, different parts of the town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we had to go to ghetto, my grandmother, mother's side, and, and us, my mother and myself, it was in one cramped condition.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But before this was happened, a last time when my father was allowed to come out of the forced labor, which I have the photo-- that was before the-- actually the yellow star they had to wear.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandmother and grandfather came from the country where they used to live, my father's side.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
